        }}></img></a></p>
    <p>{`After that show we wandered through the casino portion of the hotel (where no photography was allowed, though it didn’t look like anything special, so I don’t know why). And eventually came upon the ‘Bubble Show’, which was a 360 degree projection show. It also didn’t really have a plot that I could explain (something about dragon statues coming alive), but was a pretty cool experience and well-done in my opinion.`}</p>
