        }}></img></a></p>
    <p>{`We ended up finding a restaurant called Caton inside, and though it wasn’t very crowded (we figured most people here, weren’t going to the Venetian to eat Chinese food) the food was quite tasty! One of those many small dishes kinds of place that have a focus on quality over quantity, and kind of pricey for what we got. It was all very good though and was claiming to have won all these awards.`}</p>
